&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
To reproduce the bug do the following:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Create a user with an ID (which in my case was a user's full name)
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;
